  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 16-18 Guests</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Brigitta is located just 5 minutes' walk (500m) to the centre of Arabba and the ski lifts giving easy access to the Dolomiti Superski area. The Brigitta is tastefully designed using wood panels and warm tones and has a cosy and relaxing atmosphere. Each chalet has a dining room and small lounge area that are ideal for spending time in after a day on the slopes. The Brigitta bedrooms are furnished to a high modern alpine standard with satellite TV, fridge, and hairdryer and most have balcony. Rooms on the first, second and third floor are accessed by an external covered stairway.</p>]]></description>
