  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Accommodation Summary </strong></p>
<p><strong>Ground Floor</strong><br />Large dining area with small lounge/seating area and adjoining TV room with satelite TV.</p>
<p><strong>First Floor<br />Room 2</strong> - Twin with adjoining single room off a shared small entrance hall sharing shower/wc*.<strong><br />Rooms 3 &amp; 4</strong> - Twin with shower/wc.</p>
<p><strong>Second Floor<br />Suite 5</strong> (sleeps 2-3) - Twin with adjoining single room off a shared small entrance hall sharing shower/wc*.<strong><br />Rooms 6 &amp; 7</strong> - Twin with shower /wc.</p>
<p><strong>Third Floor</strong><br /><strong>Rooms 8 &amp; 9</strong> - Twin with shower/wc and sloping roof.</p>
<p>*Sold for triple occupancy. For double occupancy a supplement applies.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
